With digital cameras, if you are using any kind of auto focus the  
exposure may change all depending on the lighting and other factors.   
When I can&#39;t find anything to photograph I usually boost my exposure  
and use different coloured lights to create a neat light whirlwind...  
thing.  Though from what I&#39;ve heard about the Luminator people are  
using polaroids. Most now do have auto focus I believe.  I don&#39;t no  
much about polaroids or the lighting the Luminator is being used in.

Peace,
Nick
